long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides users with the ability to save the current state of a web form, then later on apply a previously saved state to that same page. This is potentially useful for QA purposes as well as any situation where a user is submitting the same form with the same values continuously.

The page is determined to be a match based on the signature it provides from its unique form inputs.
